t qu\u2019ils dorment.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"b\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_127_3\"><sup id=\"Ps.127.3\" class=\"v19_127_3\">3<\/sup>Des enfants, voil\u00e0 les vrais biens de famille,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_127_3\">la r\u00e9compense que donne le Seigneur !<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_127_4\"><sup id=\"Ps.127.4\" class=\"v19_127_4\">4<\/sup>Les fils qu\u2019un homme a dans sa jeunesse<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_127_4\">sont comme des fl\u00e8ches dans la main d\u2019un guerrier.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_127_5\"><sup id=\"Ps.127.5\" class=\"v19_127_5\">5<\/sup>Heureux l\u2019homme qui peut en remplir son carquois !<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_127_5\">Il ne risque pas d\u2019\u00eatre humili\u00e9<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_127_5\">quand il plaide contre ses adversaires \u00e0 la porte de la ville.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"b\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"127","id":"fra-FRC97:Ps.127","osis_end":"fra-FRC97:Ps.127.5","order":"19127","link":"fra-FRC97\/Ps\/127","display":"Psaumes 127","book":{"version_id":"232","name":"Psaumes","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"fra-FRC97:Ps","osis_end":"fra-FRC97:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"FRC97","version":"fra-FRC97","id":"fra-FRC97","name":"La Bible en fran\u00e7ais courant","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"fra","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>Copyright &#169; 1997, Soci&#233;t&#233; biblique fran&#231;aise. Avec autorisation. Tous droits r&#233;serv&#233;s.<\/p>","contact_url":"http:\/\/www.la-bible.net\/","audio":"NONE","sections":[{"version_id":"fra-FRC97","id":"OT","name":"Old Testament"},{"version_id":"fra-FRC97","id":"NT","name":"New Testament"}]},"audio":null,"prevChapterId":"fra-FRC97:Ps.126","nextChapterId":"fra-FRC97:Ps.128","footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]},"prevChapter":{"auditid":"0","label":"","text":"<div id=\"Ps.125\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"s1\">Ceux qui ont confiance dans le Seigneur<\/h3>\n<h3 class=\"d\">\n<sup id=\"Ps.125.1\" class=\"v19_125_1\">1<\/sup>Chant des p\u00e8lerinages.<\/h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"\">Ceux qui ont confiance dans le Seigneur<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"\">sont comme le mont Sion,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"\">qui sera toujours l\u00e0, in\u00e9branlable.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_2\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.2\" class=\"v19_125_2\">2<\/sup>J\u00e9rusalem est entour\u00e9e de montagnes ;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_2\">le Seigneur entoure aussi son peuple,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_2\">c\u2019est vrai aujourd\u2019hui, ce le sera toujours.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_3\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.3\" class=\"v19_125_3\">3<\/sup>Un gouvernement indigne<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_3\">ne pourra pas se maintenir sur la patrie des fid\u00e8les ;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_3\">autrement ceux-ci seraient tent\u00e9s de prendre part au mal.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"b\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_4\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.4\" class=\"v19_125_4\">4<\/sup>Seigneur, montre-toi bon<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_4\">pour ceux que tu trouves bons,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_4\">pour les hommes au c\u0153ur droit.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"b\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_5\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.5\" class=\"v19_125_5\">5<\/sup>Quant \u00e0 ceux qui suivent des voies tortueuses,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_5\">tu devrais les balayer, Seigneur,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_5\">avec ceux qui font le malheur des autres !<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"b\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v19_125_5\">Que la paix soit donn\u00e9e \u00e0 Isra\u00ebl !<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"b\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"125","id":"fra-FRC97:Ps.125","osis_end":"fra-FRC97:Ps.125.5","order":"19125","link":"fra-FRC97\/Ps\/125","display":"Psaumes 125","book":{"version_id":"232","name":"Psaumes","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"fra-FRC97:Ps","osis_end":"fra-FRC97:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"FRC97","version":"fra-FRC97","id":"fra-FRC97","name":"La Bible en fran\u00e7ais courant","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"fra","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>Copyright &#169; 1997, Soci&#233;t&#233; biblique fran&#231;aise. Avec autorisation. Tous droits r&#233;serv&#233;s.<\/p>","contact_url":"http:\/\/www.la-bible.net\/","audio":"NONE","sections":[{"version_id":"fra-FRC97","id":"OT","name":"Old Testament"},{"version_id":"fra-FRC97","id":"NT","name":"New Testament"}]},"audio":null,"prevChapterId":"fra-FRC97:Ps.124","nextChapterId":"fra-FRC97:Ps.126","footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]},"footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]}